      "body": "@terrykingcha do you have a real example about ins lifecycle? My opinion on Weex instance lifecycle APIs is:\n\n**APIs to Renderer**\n- call `createFinish` in `dom` module when `createInstance`\n- call `refreshFinish` in `dom` module when `refreshInstance`\n- call `destroyFinish` in `dom` module when `destroyInstance`\n- `fireEvent` and `callback` has no more calls\n\n**APIs for DSL**\n- `<embed>` events: `<embed src=\"...\" oncreate=\"...\" onchange=\"...\" ondestroy=\"...\">`\n"
    },
