  "body": "# Lifecycle\n## workflow\n### createInstance\n\n![createInstance](http://gw.alicdn.com/mt/TB1NL3tJVXXXXaLXVXXXXXXXXXX-1024-768.jpg)\n### refreshInstance\n\n![refreshInstance](http://gw.alicdn.com/mt/TB1HsoQJVXXXXcyXXXXXXXXXXXX-1024-768.jpg)\n### fireEvent/callback\n\n![fireEvent/callback](http://gw.alicdn.com/mt/TB1BKUFJVXXXXXIXFXXXXXXXXXX-1024-768.jpg)\n### destoryInstance\n\n![destoryInstance](http://gw.alicdn.com/mt/TB1je7BJVXXXXbyXFXXXXXXXXXX-1024-768.jpg)\n### navigate\n\n![navigate](http://gw.alicdn.com/mt/TB1YTwmJVXXXXb6XVXXXXXXXXXX-1024-768.jpg)\n## The API for Native\n\n``` javascript\n/**\n * @param {string} instanceId - the instance id\n * @param {string} name - the notified name(appear/disppear/destory/created/updated/refreshed)\n * @param {object} options - any options\n */\nglobal.notifyInstance(instanceId, name, options)\n```\n## The API in DSL\n\n``` javascript\n/**\n * @param {string} name - the notified name\n * @param {function} callback - call when notified\n */\nvm.$observe(name, callback)\n```\n"
